name: Yogitoes® - "Awareness" SKIDLESS® Yoga Towels
description:
A super absorbent, hygienic layer SKIDLESS® Yogitoes® Yoga Towel to place on your yoga mat to prevent slipping.

How to use

Place nub side down on top of your yoga mat at the start of your practice. or if traveling or doing a home practice, place straight on to the floor. The nubs will do the work for you. 
When distributing your weight equally between hands and feet the DOTS will grip directly into the mat. 
Yogis using rental or communal yoga mats should definitely get a yoga towel for extra protection from possible skin infections.
